13	18	1	2026	{"alumni_activities": "<h2><strong>Higher Education Data Collected:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>A total of 108 higher education records, along with all supporting documents, were compiled by January 2026.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Alumni Portal Updates:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>The total number of alumni registered on the VNRVJET Alumni Portal (<a target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\\" href=\\"http://www.vnralums.com\\">www.vnralums.com</a>) is <strong>21,169.</strong></p></li><li><p>The Alumni Association circulated New Year&nbsp;wishes to all alumni.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Alumni Association Monthly Meeting:</strong></h2><p>The Executive Committee, Alumni Coordination Committee, and SARC Team meeting was held on January 24, 2026. The discussions focused on key topics, including</p><ul><li><p><strong>Top 10 Alumni Influencers: </strong>Identification of top 10 alumni influencers for each department from the 1999-2009 batches.</p></li><li><p><strong>Distinguished Spotlight Podcast: </strong>Announcement regarding the scheduled release of the podcast this weekend.</p></li><li><p><strong>Mentoring Program Coordination: </strong>Organization of alumni participation in mentoring programs, targeting four mentors per month from each department.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Student Ambassadors _ Graduating 2026 Batch</strong>:</h2><ul><li><p>As part of our ongoing efforts to strengthen connections between our current students and the alumni community, we launched the <strong>Batch Ambassador Program</strong> for the <strong>2026 graduating batch</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Each department is requested to nominate one student representative from each section by 2nd February 2026.</p></li><li><p>Batch Ambassadors will serve as key representatives of their respective cohorts, fostering engagement, strengthening communication, and building a lifelong alumni network even before graduation.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Top 10 Influencers from Alumni Batches 199